      </li>
      <li class="community-section-features-item">
        <img src='<%= static_url(@conn, "/images/icon-large-bolt.svg") %>' width="60" height="60" alt="Bolt Icon">
        <span>Exclusive features for community members</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="community" class="community-section">
    <header class="community-section-header">
      <i><img src='<%= static_url(@conn, "/images/community/slack-mark.svg") %>' width="60" height="60" alt="Slack Logomark"></i>
      <h2>Slack Everyday with&nbsp;Friends</h2>
      <p>Connect with like-minded developers from all over the world. Hang with us and Slack in realtime during our live shows. Be the first to hear about upcoming shows and projects. This is your all-access pass to everything we do.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="community-section-content community-section-content--slack">
      <div class="community-section-content-image">
        <img src='<%= static_url(@conn, "/images/community/slack-screenshot.jpg") %>' alt="Screenshot of a Slack channel conversation.">
      </div>
      <div class="community-section-content-info">
        <div class="community-section-content-info-top">
          <h3>There are no imposters&nbsp;here.</h3>
          <p>Everyone is welcome. You are not an imposter. No matter where you are on your hacker path &mdash; this community is a safe place for you to hang your hat and call home. All you have to do is take the first step.</p>
          <p><%= link "Join the community", to: page_path(@conn, :join), title: "Join the community" %>&nbsp;&nbsp;ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥ðŸ”¥</p>
        </div>

        <div class="community-section-content-info-bottom">
          <blockquote class="community-quote">
            <div class="community-quote-body">
              <p>There's no way to truely say how much value I get from being a part of Changelog Community. I'm there everyday, and there's always something being discussed by the community. It's&nbsp;awesome.</p>
            </div>
            <footer class="community-quote-footer">
              <a href="https://twitter.com/jdorfman" title="Justin Dorfman on Twitter">
                <img src='<%= static_url(@conn, "/images/community/justin-dorfman.jpg") %>' alt="A smiling man in a ballcap and glasses." width="65" height="65">
                <strong>Justin Dorfman</strong>
                <span class="quote-title">Developer Relations at Sticker Mule</span>
              </a>
            </footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

